fields.name: Sony - WH-CH710N Wireless Noise-Cancelling Over-the-Ear Headphones - Black
fields.description: Turn down the world's noise with the long-lasting noise cancellation performance of the WH-CH710N wireless headphones. Dual Noise Sensor technology automatically senses your environment to deliver an amazing sound experience. With up to 35 hours of battery life¹, quick charging, and access to your smartphone's voice assistant², the WH-CH710N are sure to be a must-have for your travels.

fields.name: JLab Audio - JBuds Air True Wireless Earbud Headphones - Black
fields.description: Enjoy your workout and travel playlists with these JBuds Air true wireless earbuds. Three EQ settings include JLab Signature, Balanced and Bass Boost to customize your listening experience, and the charging case provides 10 hours of additional battery life. Take clear, hands-free phone calls with the built-in microphone and Bluetooth 5.0 technology of these JBuds Air true wireless earbuds.

fields.name: Bose - Sport Earbuds – True Wireless Bluetooth In-Ear Headphones - Triple Black
fields.description: Bose Sport Earbuds are true wireless Bluetooth earbuds engineered to produce clear and balanced sound in any listening environment. StayHear™ Max tips mold to your ears with soft silicone and won’t fall out, no matter how demanding your workout is. Bose Sport Earbuds go through rigorous quality testing for durability and will resist moisture from sweat and weather. And instead of buttons, a capacitive touch interface lets you simply tap to play or pause music, answer calls, and more. With a battery life of up to five hours get ready to beat your personal best, again and again.

fields.name: Audio-Technica - Audio Technica ATH-AWKT Closed-Back Wood Headphone - Black
fields.description: The ATH-AWKT over-ear wooden headphones feature housings made from the rare Japanese hardwood Kokutan (striped ebony). Long used for woodwind instruments and pianos, this dense wood with the handsome black and brown stripes suppresses unwanted resonance to deliver clear, natural sound reproduction. The half-gloss finish, applied by hand, brings out the natural beauty of the wood’s grain – a beauty that will only deepen with age.

fields.name: Onkyo - 6-Disc CD Player - Black
fields.description: Listen to your favorite albums with this Onkyo DX-C390(B) 6-disc CD player that features Vector Linear Shaping Circuitry technology for clear, brilliant audio. The high-precision multibit D/A converter delivers high-quality sound.

fields.name: Panasonic - Streaming 4K Ultra HD Hi-Res Audio with Dolby Vision 7.1 Channel DVD/CD/3D Wi-Fi Built-In Blu-Ray Player - Black
fields.description: Enjoy brilliant color and sound with this Panasonic Ultra HD Blu-ray player. The chroma processing technology maximizes the color of 4K/HDR content, and the 7.1-channel audio output produces lifelike surround sound when connected to a home audio system. The color signals received by this Panasonic Ultra HD Blu-ray player are upgraded to produce natural textures and depth.

fields.name: Insignia™ - 3' 3.5mm Audio Cable - Black
fields.description: This 3' Insignia™ NS-LW16 3.5mm audio cable lets you connect a cell phone, tablet or MP3 player to a stereo system, speaker or computer and features a low-profile design that enables easy connectivity while your device remains in its case.

fields.name: Rocketfish™ - 30' 16 Gauge CM Speaker Wire - Gold
fields.description: You’ve purchased a high-quality sound system for your entertainment center, and now only one thing remains: putting it all together and achieving that perfect sound. Some would say it’s the most daunting part of the whole process, especially when a bad cable can make your audio experience fall flat. This Rocketfish 30' 16 Gauge CM Speaker Wire makes the job simple.

fields.name: AudioQuest - OptiLink Cinnamon 9.8' In-Wall Optical Cable - Red
fields.description: This 9.8' AudioQuest OptiLink Cinnamon OPTCIN03 in-wall optical cable offers simple connectivity and features high-purity polymer fiber and highly polished ends for reduced internal and termination reflections.

fields.name: Insignia™ - 12' A/V Cable - Black
fields.description: Use this 12-foot Insignia composite audio/video cable to attach devices over distances. The three specialized connectors provide the best quality for both sound and picture.

fields.name: Audio-Technica - ATLP120XBT Bluetooth Stereo Turntable - Black
fields.description: Play your favorite records with this Audio-Technica wireless turntable. Bluetooth technology lets you pair speakers or headphones for a wireless listening experience, while the RCA cable connects to your home stereo for high-quality sound. This Audio-Technica wireless turntable has a DC servo direct-drive motor and an adjustable anti-skate control to play 33 13, 45 and 78 rpm records smoothly.

fields.name: Sony - Bluetooth Stereo Turntable - Black
fields.description: Enjoy timeless vinyl in modern quality with this Sony wireless turntable. Bluetooth connectivity pushes high-quality audio to wireless speakers and headphones, while a built-in phono audio output ensures wired devices can be connected as well. A minimalist design simplifies use of this Sony wireless turntable to a single button press, and two operating speeds allow for customizable playback.

fields.name: Victrola - Bluetooth Stereo Audio System - Gold/Brown/Black
fields.description: Play records, CDs and FM radio with this seven-in-one Victrola Bluetooth record player. The three-speed turntable lets you record from vinyl to MP3 with the included software. This Victrola Bluetooth record player has built-in stereo, 3.5mm aux-in, RCA output and headphone jack for compatibility with most accessories.

fields.name: Studebaker - Bluetooth Stereo Audio System - High Gloss Black
fields.description: Spin your favorite tunes with this Studebaker turntable. Its low-profile design updates a classic look while providing the same functionality as vintage record players, and the Bluetooth connectivity is ideal for audio streaming. This Studebaker turntable has an auxiliary port for smartphones and other compatible devices to maximize listening options.
